        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Step into effortless style and unparalleled comfort with The Number 33 x Lusso Cloud Scenario Slide, a collaboration inspired by the vibrant charm of fresh florals and fruits at your favorite local market. This limited-edition slide features a stunning all-over floral print on Lusso Cloud's signature Scenario silhouette, making it the perfect go-to for on and off the course.</p><p>But there's more—every purchase includes a complimentary pack of exclusive The Number 33 x Lusso Cloud Apricot Tee Picks, adding a flavorful touch to your golf game and beyond.</p>"
          }
        }
