        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Scenario Slide isn't just about looks—it's designed for all-day comfort and durability. Lightweight and breathable, these slides feature molded arch support and a textured interior to prevent blisters. The water-friendly design and flex groove outsole ensure traction on wet surfaces, making them ideal for wherever your day takes you.</p>"
